a` is used (cloned on demand).\\n- `--metrics-repo-path`: optional path to the metrics repository root. If omitted, a default clone under `local_repositories/metadata-forge-metrics` is used (cloned on demand).\\n- `--docs-path`: optional directory with read-only docs for agent context (e.g., extracted Javadoc).\\n\\nExample:\\n```bash\\npython3 ai_workflows/add_new_library_support.py \\\\\\n  --coordinates org.example:lib:1.2.3 \\\\\\n  --reachability-metadata-path /path/to/graalvm-reachability-metadata \\\\\\n  --metrics-repo-path /path/to/metrics-storage \\\\\\n  --docs-path /path/to/docs\\n```\\n\\nOptions:\\n- `--strategy-name NAME` select a predefined workflow strategy from `strategies/predefined_strategies.json`. Defaults to \\\"basic_iterative\\\".\\n\\n[362 more lines in file. Use offset=121 to continue.]\"}], \"isError\": false, \"timestamp\": 1777427711646}}\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge1/metadata-forge/logs/org.jetbrains.kotlinx:atomicfu:0.19.0/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-04-29T01-56-55-311489Z.log:300:  ./build/agent-artifact-discovery-logs/org.jetbrains.kotlinx-atomicfu-0.19.0.log\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge1/metadata-forge/logs/org.jetbrains.kotlinx:atomicfu:0.19.0/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-04-29T01-56-55-311489Z.log:301:  ./build/discovered-artifact-metadata/org.jetbrains.kotlinx-atomicfu-0.19.0.json\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge1/metadata-forge/logs/org.jetbrains.kotlinx:atomicfu:0.19.0/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-04-29T01-56-55-311489Z.log:302:  ./build/tests/org.jetbrains.kotlinx:atomicfu:0.19.0/0fbb77ac4a267d46308e849a5a0c893f.out\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge1/metadata-forge/logs/org.jetbrains.kotlinx:atomicfu:0.19.0/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-04-29T01-56-55-311489Z.log:303:  ./metadata/org.jetbrains.kotlinx/atomicfu/0.19.0/reachability-metadata.json\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge1/metadata-forge/logs/org.jetbrains.kotlinx:atomicfu:0.19.0/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-04